      "value": "<p>Your blood or other vital fluids clot quickly, reducing the chance of ongoing danger.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Con 13</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> Whenever you take bleed damage, reduce it by half your Constitution bonus ([[/ max(0, floor(@abilities.con.mod / 2))]]). If this would reduce the damage to 0, the bleeding condition ends. The DC to administer @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.d4fcGwOcrsuYrwGH#first-aid]{first aid} to you to end bleeding effects is reduced by 5.</p>"
